{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e9d175e4c7","title":"要改革制度","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"898c0c3540","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"e9d175e4c7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"1b6d6991fb","name":"叶于泩"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d45196eb95","type":"title","text":"要改革制度","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9d175e4c7"},{"id":"ab32bd413b","type":"authors","text":"北京大学叶于泩","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9d175e4c7"},{"id":"6892777e9c","type":"subtitle","text":"（叶于泩：北京大学哲学系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9d175e4c7"},{"id":"f91eca7a85","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）整风只能是第一步，必须改革制度来巩固战果，继续扩大我国社会主义民主。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9d175e4c7"},{"id":"c62fd4520b","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）官僚主义、宗派主义、主观主义的滋生有其历史社会根源的，“除三害”必须依靠全国人民群众，作经常的长期的斗争。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9d175e4c7"},{"id":"8a18cedbd0","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）事实证明关键不在群众，不是没有意见，而是不敢提；不是没提意见，而是不理睬，甚至压制。不是没有好意见，而是被埋没。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9d175e4c7"},{"id":"c985c2c041","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）为了保护和鼓励群众除三害的积极性，必须从立法上给予实际的保证，必须改革制度，加强其民主性。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9d175e4c7"},{"id":"ef0c7b6ee6","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）除三害既是长期的任务，就不能“一阵风”，这就必须有一个切实可行的制度经常起保证作用。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9d175e4c7"},{"id":"125f1837be","type":"paragraph","text":"（六）改革制度，不是不要社会主义，相反的是要保卫它、加强它，必须在保卫公有制和无产阶级专政的前提下，把国家制度中的不民主的东西改革掉。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9d175e4c7"},{"id":"f4b6edbd97","type":"paragraph","text":"（七）制度并不是好看好听的条文，好的制度，必须保证它自身的实现，要加强制度的对自身的保证。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9d175e4c7"},{"id":"461cebc11d","type":"paragraph","text":"（八）我国民主化的现状落后于形势的发展，这是斯大林错误的恶果之一，改革制度必须朝向民主化的方向。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9d175e4c7"},{"id":"3ad2c8a64d","type":"paragraph","text":"（九）在社会主义旗帜下的全面开放，包括政治上的开放，发展马克思主义的开放。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9d175e4c7"},{"id":"f119411982","type":"paragraph","text":"（十）加强人民群众对国家机关的监督，确保民主权利的实际行使。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9d175e4c7"},{"id":"3f005f689d","type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义万岁！","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9d175e4c7"},{"id":"ececcbbd3c","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9d175e4c7"}],"page":{"id":"dffa8f4dba","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e9d175e4c7","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}